Investors

Questions and communications regarding UTC's financial performance should be addressed to Investor Relations.
 
Investor Relations phone: (860) 728-7000Email: [email protected]
Mailing Address:
Investor RelationsUnited Technologies Corporation10 Farm Springs Rd.Farmington, CT 06032
Questions and communications regarding transfer of stock, replacement of lost certificates, dividends, dividend reinvestment, stock purchase plan and address changes should be addressed to Computershare, who serves as registrar and transfer agent for UTC's Common Stock.
Computershare can be contacted at: (800) 488-9281
Click here for online access to stockholder accounts through Computershare. (Note: This link will launch a new window to a third-party website. Close the window when you're finished viewing the information.)
Although UTC does not have direct access to shareowner records maintained by Computershare, in some cases UTC Shareowner Relations is also able to assist with shareowner questions. UTC Shareowner Relations can be contacted at:
Shareowner Relations phone: (860) 728-7870
Email: [email protected]​​​
