Ombudsman Program

From within the United States, Canada and Puerto Rico, call 800.871.9065.
When calling from outside the United States, you must first dial the pertinent AT&T Direct access code found here​. Listen for a prompt (voice or tone), and then dial the toll-free number for an Ombudsman. Interpreters will be provided through the Ombudsman if English is not your preferred language.
All translators used by the Ombudsman program are retained to work for the Ombudsman and under contract are also obligated to protect confidentiality. Confidential Ombudsman information is secured and accessible only by Ombudsman personnel.​
Website: ombudsman.confidential.utc.com​​
Close

